sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    User ->> AuthenticationController: POST /api/v1/auth/passwordless/request (or /login/passwordless/request)
    AuthenticationController ->> PasswordlessLoginService: requestPasswordlessLogin(email)
    PasswordlessLoginService -->> AuthenticationController: completion
    AuthenticationController -->> User: 200 ApiResponse {message: "Passwordless login link sent if the email is registered"}
